== Month of Kanotomi (辛巳) == In the Gregorian calendar, during years ending in 0 or 5 (where the {{ill|Heavenly Stems|lt=Ten Heavenly Stems|ja|十干|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} are {{ill|Kō (庚)|ja|庚|1=Kanoe (庚)|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} or {{ill|Otsu (乙)|ja|乙|1=Kinoto (乙)|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}), the fourth month (April) is the Kanotomi month. Note that this can refer to the month in the {{ill|Lunisolar calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} or the “solar term” month (from {{ill|Rikka|ja|立夏|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} to the day before {{ill|Bōshu|ja|芒種|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}).
== Day of Kanotomi (辛巳) == A Kanotomi day is associated with the following selection day (選日).
